          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 3.39-MeV state in B12 has been studied in the",
                "B12+n system, where the state appears as a resonance",
                "at a (lab) neutron energy of 20.8+-0.5 keV.",
                "Scattering and transmission measurements were",
                "compared with 11B(d,p) data and were used to",
                "determine that resonance was d-wave. Spin J=3-",
                "determined by ruling out other alternatives. For each",
                "possible j value a neutron width was calculated from",
                "the data."
              ]
            }
          ],
