                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The apparatus has been used in a number of fast",
                "neutron experiments. A sample, which may or may not",
                "consist of the element being investigated, scatters",
                "the neutrons into a system of moderated BF3 counters.",
                "Another sample can be placed in front of the entire",
                "system so that transmission measurements are possible",
                "as well. Background is measured by removing the",
                "scattering sample. All sample changing is remotely",
                "controlled."
              ]
